            . Last Monday was se'nnight, about four in the afternoon, I was in <placeName id="t17641017-16-crimeloc88">Cornhill, above the 'Change</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17641017-16-crimeloc88" type="placeName" value="Cornhill, above the 'Change"></interp>
